-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.
select * from
(select toDate(time) as date,count(distinct user_id) from simulator_20221020.message_actions group by date) as msg_stat
JOIN 
(select toDate(time) as date, count(distinct user_id) from simulator_20221020.feed_actions group by date) as feed_stat
using date

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.
select date,msg/feed as attitude from
(select toDate(time) as date,count(distinct user_id) as msg from simulator_20221020.message_actions group by date) as msg_stat
JOIN 
(select toDate(time) as date, count(distinct user_id) as feed from simulator_20221020.feed_actions group by date) as feed_stat
using date

(select * from simulator_20221020.feed_actions ) t1
JOIN 
(select * from simulator_20221020.message_actions ) t2
using user_id
